These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, goat, frog, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, cricket, swimming, surfing, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##5
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the turtle##7
 7. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
10. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
11. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
12. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
14. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the goat##7
15. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
16. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's sport is swimming##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Pet           | frog | lizard | rat | hamster | turtle | goat |
| Sport   | rugby | cricket    | baseball  | surfing  | swimming            | skiing  |

