.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, rugby, basketball, rowing, ice-hockey
City: new-york, venice, hannover, san-francisco, nizza, edinburgh
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
 3. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person traveling to venice##2
 6. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person traveling to hannover##8
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
13. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
15. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Sport   | rugby | ice-hockey | soccer | rowing | basketball | badminton |
| City     | hannover  | new-york  | venice         | edinburgh | nizza    | san-francisco   |

