.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku, traveling, baking, reading, photography
The people have 6 different jobs:  police-officer, photographer, coach, scientist, dancer, social-worker
 1. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 3. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 4. the coach is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 7. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
10. the scientist is on the far right##1
11. the social-worker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the coach##7
12. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
13. the person who's hobby is photography is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
15. the coach is somewhere between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
16. the dancer is not to the left of the dancer##8
17. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
18. the person who's hobby is reading is the photographer##1
19. the coach is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
