.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
House: cape-cod, wooden, townhouse, ranch-style, victorian, palace
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, coral, pink, mauve, black, grey
 1. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the wooden house##8
 2. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
 3. the palace house is between the person who likes apricot and the cape-cod house##2
 4. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
 5. the palace house is somewhere between the victorian house and the person who likes coral##7
 6. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 7. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 8. the person who likes black is not to the left of the palace house##8
 9. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
10. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
11. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
12. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the palace house##7
13. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
14. the wooden house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
15. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4
16. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
17. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| House    | cape-cod | palace    | victorian     | ranch-style  | wooden    | townhouse |
| Color   | coral  | black | apricot | grey | pink | mauve     |

