The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, march, september, august, june, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda | 7up | almond-milk | milk    | lemonade |
| Birthday     | april   | january  | march   | august  | september | june    |

