.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-18::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, february, june, march, november, may
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, video-games, magic-tricks, singing, sudoku
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
11. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
13. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
15. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
16. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
17. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |   3    |  4   |      5      |   6    |
| Birthday   | november     | march  | may | april  | february | june  |
| Hobby       | board-games | video-games | sudoku | singing | cooking | magic-tricks |

